dct_title_s: Topographical map of the city of Newark, Essex County, N.J. Drawn from surveys made by order of the Common Council
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially and by shading, hachures and spot heights. Includes inset map of environs of Newark, Explanations, Statistics of Newark and Historical data. Indexed for points of interest. Wall map, mounted on wooden rollers.
